        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Calling this function is equivalent to <programlisting filename=".c"><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="group___app_focus_service_1ga519e14f1ff52ade4c3a3ccdf04825460" kindref="member">app_focus_service_subscribe_handlers</ref>((<ref refid="struct_app_focus_handlers" kindref="compound">AppFocusHandlers</ref>){</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>.will_focus<sp/>=<sp/>handler,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">});</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Out focus events are triggered when a modal window is about to open and cover the app. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>In focus events are triggered when a modal window which is covering the app is about to close. </para>
</simplesect>
